  <name>Tabular</name>
  <summary>SQL and NoSQL database client</summary>
  
  <description>
    <p>
      Tabular helps you explore and query SQL and NoSQL databases from a single desktop app.
      Connect to PostgreSQL, MySQL, SQLite, MongoDB, Redis, and Microsoft SQL Server.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Support for multiple database types</li>
      <li>Fast and efficient query execution</li>
      <li>Data export capabilities</li>
      <li>SSH tunnel support</li>
      <li>Built with Rust for performance and safety</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
  
